WEBVTT

00:10.041 --> 00:13.291
<i>It's a brand-new year</i>
<i>in sweet home Chicago.</i>

00:13.375 --> 00:17.416
<i>And one of the perks of having a rooftop</i>
<i>that looks directly into Wrigley Field</i>

00:17.500 --> 00:19.916
<i>is that you get to experience Opening Day.</i>

00:20.750 --> 00:24.666
<i>Not the first game, but when the guys</i>
<i>with the huge hoses show up.</i>

00:24.750 --> 00:28.125
<i>I'm talking about</i>
<i>the groundskeepers, baby!</i>

00:28.625 --> 00:32.000
<i>For years, me and my neighbors</i>
<i>would watch every home game</i>

00:32.083 --> 00:35.250
<i>while partying</i>
<i>our respective wieners and clams off.</i>

00:35.333 --> 00:36.958
<i>God, those were good times.</i>

00:37.041 --> 00:41.666
<i>Sure, most of the old gang</i>
<i>moved to the suburbs or got jobs,</i>

00:41.750 --> 00:43.416
<i>but I'm still here</i>

00:43.500 --> 00:48.125
<i>and I ain't lettin' nothing stop me</i>
<i>from keeping this badass tradition alive!</i>

00:50.666 --> 00:52.833
Lay that sod, Bernice!

00:52.916 --> 00:54.666
-Nice form!

00:54.750 --> 00:56.416
How great is this, Daniel?

00:56.500 --> 00:57.875
