10:54.458 --> 10:56.166
Oh my God, I'm so sorry.

10:56.250 --> 10:58.458
I'm actually a little busy right now.

10:58.541 --> 11:00.458
-Is that Fucks Loud Sophie?

11:00.541 --> 11:02.750
Wow, even Wet Hair Lady is here.

11:02.833 --> 11:05.000
Wait, are all the neighbors here?

11:05.083 --> 11:06.875
Yeah. They all just came by.

11:06.958 --> 11:08.041
So random.

11:08.125 --> 11:09.000
Oh.

11:09.083 --> 11:10.583
So, should I come in?

11:10.666 --> 11:13.833
Ah, well, we kind of
paired off for charades.

11:13.916 --> 11:16.791
Maybe it's more fun
if we… hung out later on?

11:16.875 --> 11:18.416
-Is that cool?
-Uh…

11:18.500 --> 11:20.083
Yeah! So cool.

11:20.166 --> 11:21.250
Awesome sauce!

11:22.000 --> 11:25.416
Oh my God, Mr. Jorgavich,
you're my spirit animal.

11:26.291 --> 11:30.333
And then I realized six hours later,
you don't pair off for charades!

11:30.416 --> 11:32.583
Did I do something wrong to Amanda?

11:32.666 --> 11:35.500
Did I offend her somehow?
Should I be offended?

11:35.583 --> 11:38.583
Child, it is not <i>possible</i>
for you to be offended.

11:38.666 --> 11:39.916
Because you lack--

11:40.000 --> 11:41.666
